# Core Theme Principles

- **WordPress Coding Standards**: Follow WordPress PHP, CSS, JavaScript, and HTML coding standards
- **Template Hierarchy**: Use proper WordPress template hierarchy (specific to general)
- **Security First**: Always sanitize input, escape output, use nonces for forms
- **Performance**: Optimize assets (enqueue properly, minify, use caching)
- **Accessibility**: Follow WCAG guidelines - semantic HTML, ARIA labels, keyboard navigation
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach, test all breakpoints
- **No Business Logic**: Themes are for presentation only - complex logic belongs in plugins
- **Child Theme Compatible**: Build themes that can be safely extended with child themes
